Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機場!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚嗚嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知弦 杉崎欺負我說我是飛機場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖～乖～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.29,0:16:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Key君 攻擊人的身體特徵是最不為人所齒的低級趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.81,0:16:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 男生總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥 這種像稍微有點煩人的同班女生一樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.40,0:17:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖 沒關係啦 有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚嗚嗚 知弦什麼的最討厭啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉Key君 我好像也覺得有點麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.65,0:17:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小真冬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,備用品的確認完畢了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還有其他工作 所以打算先做那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.59,0:17:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更新攻略wiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是只有真冬才能勝任的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別人也會做的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種想法 是會折磨苦苦搜尋攻略的廣大玩家的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:39.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種人就折磨一下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 學長竟然是這樣的人...真冬我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.87,0:17:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真冬寫的攻略能拯救誰的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算耽擱自己的工作也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:18:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打比方的話 就像給瀕死的魔物輸送治癒之力而自己卻倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟這事件是一個性質的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.96,0:18:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~深夏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那傢伙也偷懶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊啊 不准過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾一邊去 你這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為演劇部有遞交申請 我只是穿穿看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.81,0:18:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的嫁！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然離滿18歲還有一年連名義上的都做不成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我講啊 都說了只是穿穿看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然傲嬌是王道 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嬌你個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.44,0:18:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然挺暴露的 不過在接受範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知弦姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久候多時了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的真心是否屬實 能證明給我看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:18:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好歹是主角吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.93,0:19:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,697號怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 找不到446號了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,446號...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有什麼我可以幫忙的...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯...找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.15,0:19:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒術研究會 五寸釘和人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.71,0:19:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否決
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紅 這邊不快點解決的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手已經很疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可不行喔 已經接手了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,765號 輕音部 響板 OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是別的文件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 先等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.29,0:19:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.40,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉崎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉崎學長生氣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.34,0:20:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他老是嬉皮笑臉不好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.15,0:20:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.58,0:20:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許是過分了點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.53,0:20:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣學生會的工作也能順利進展
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.26,0:20:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和各部門以及學校交涉後把文件整理在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是 會長 麻煩你蓋章
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.06,0:20:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛機場
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.61,0:20:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼快把點心擺出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後和以往一樣 和我談情說愛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.34,0:20:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不記得有這檔子事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杉崎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺大家不該眉頭緊鎖地做事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.53,0:20:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟這裡是我的後宮嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.03,0:20:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到離校時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 明明才要開始
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的學生會到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是和往常一樣的學生會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紅不喜歡現在學生會的氛圍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.46,0:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.14,0:21:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真冬也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然探索新活動很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但因此學生會失去溫暖的話會很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫暖?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.55,0:21:47.76,*Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 請大家慢用 杉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認可
